data.description: Open House* 12/15 Fri: 11-2pm and 12/16 Sat: 11-2pm*    Beautiful home with lots of space to entertain in a gated community with a lovely front yard. Enter into an open floor plan with living room and a huge island kitchen with plenty of space to gather around! The backyard boasts a huge deck with an outdoor kitchen that includes grill, mini fridge, color changing lights and counter space to cook! Upstairs you will find a nice size Media/Theater room with Screen, Speakers, and Projector System - Included!!  Chair, Couch and loveseats in media room also Included. There is a secondary down stairs with a full bathroom. This is a must see house! Well maintained and loved with lots of nice colors and touches.
